The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the problem of blind motion deblurring. The use of deep neural networks and generative adversarial networks is also mentioned, indicating a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.GR (Graphics).
